{"tid":2213164,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"佩洛西不排除再彈劾特朗普 阻大法官提名","createTime":"2020-09-22T10:33:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-22T14:20:47.000Z","uid":75656,"like":6,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"b77441d86682cde1f3998b600d192ae588274df7","tid":2213164,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T10:33:12.000Z","msg":"美國民主黨籍國會眾議院議長佩洛西表示，不排除以彈劾總統特朗普作為手段，阻止他提名最高法院大法官人選。<br />\n<br />\n她接受美國廣播公司訪問時，沒有否定關於民主黨以彈劾特朗普或司法部長巴爾(Bill Barr)，作為阻止參議院審理大法官替補人選的可能性。她稱，有很多選項，但不準備討論任何細節，只是議員有責任要根據憲法賦與的一切權力，確保美國憲法的尊嚴及美國的民主。<br />\n<br />\n白宮副新聞秘書Brian Morgenstern回應指，特朗普只是按照憲法授予的權力作出提名，如果因此被彈劾，將是很危險的舉措。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2587352/%E4%BD%A9%E6%B4%9B%E8%A5%BF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8E%92%E9%99%A4%E5%86%8D%E5%BD%88%E5%8A%BE%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE+%E9%98%BB%E5%A4%A7%E6%B3%95%E5%AE%98%E6%8F%90%E5%90%8D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2587352%2F%25E4%25BD%25A9%25E6%25B4%259B%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258E%2592%25E9%2599%25A4%25E5%2586%258D%25E5%25BD%2588%25E5%258A%25BE%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2599%25AE%2B%25E9%2598%25BB%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25AE%2598%25E6%258F%2590%25E5%2590%258D&d=o%2BIu8jl9TkUz6xxK8T5I20Bo7c%2BYFxEppcXi0rJe94o%3D&h=0ff52688\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2587352/%E4%BD%A9%E6%B4%9B%E8%A5%BF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8E%92%E9%99%A4%E5%86%8D%E5%BD%88%E5%8A%BE%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE+%E9%98%BB%E5%A4%A7%E6%B3%95%E5%AE%98%E6%8F%90%E5%90%8D</a>"},{"pid":"71dd7b6a4003a9ef7b02776467a915b09908a9cc","tid":2213164,"uid":55043,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T10:40:41.000Z","msg":"又幫china joe倒米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc8a8ee1d6074a67d61240b8488599835a540440","tid":2213164,"uid":87757,"like":11,"dislike":8,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T10:43:25.000Z",